{"data":[{"id":561197435,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"893cfb82a7fb36f5ef906abe2aa5d169","url_token":"qin-zheng-18-3","name":"mooore","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ab6d65d9f6b5fe39154a6c2e390452dd_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ab6d65d9f6b5fe39154a6c2e390452dd_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/893cfb82a7fb36f5ef906abe2aa5d169","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":5,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561197435","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545925695,"updated_time":1545927162,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"comment_count":4,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e看了一些支持他的人，有的说不要打击一个少年对数学的热爱。年轻人有理想是个好事。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我认为这是对那些真正有理想，踏实工作的青年科研人员的侮辱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个高三学生不认真备考，整天满脑子想些不切实际的幻想。另外我认为与其让他钻进牛角尖，不如称早浇灭不切实际的幻想去认真复习更为重要。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外麻烦那些支持他的人学习一下高等数学后再来发表看法好吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实自己上面的言论有些过激了。高中压力确实大，每个人都有彷徨的时候。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实对于题主这样偏科比较严重的，一味试图通过证明哥德巴赫猜想来获取名校资格，有点走火入魔。与其费劲心思的证明哥德巴赫猜想，还不如把这时间用来补习其他弱势学科。我感觉这条路更有用。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哪怕自己高考成绩不理想，你也可以去一个普通的本科院校。大学时你就可以学习高等数学， 可以获取更多数学知识。而且到时候你可以选择考研。到时候研究哥德巴赫猜想不是比现在更加靠谱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我父亲以前对我说过：什么年龄就要做什么年龄应该做的事情。现在你最好的选择就是好好备考。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你现在证明哥德巴赫猜想只是为了获取一个保送名校的机会。那么对不起，请不要侮辱热爱与梦想。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"看了一些支持他的人，有的说不要打击一个少年对数学的热爱。年轻人有理想是个好事。我认为这是对那些真正有理想，踏实工作的青年科研人员的侮辱。一个高三学生不认真备考，整天满脑子想些不切实际的幻想。另外我认为与其让他钻进牛角尖，不如称早浇灭不切实…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1674\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%